First you have to create a directory called src, and then put your data in this directory. Each class should put in one directory, such 0, 1, 2, 3..., then run simplerename.
Then create three directory, train, verify and test. run the rebuild.py, and input the percent of train , verify and test like: 70, 15, 15.
Run binAndCrop to bin and crop the images.
Finally, run createDataSet.py to create the pkl.gz file.
